divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside on my pario near midnight.I saw a strange slow light coming across the sky toward our house (high above). As it got closer I realized it had boomberang shaped light on the front. As is slowly made its way above me I noticed the rest of the object was a dull dark greay sphere. It was quite large in size. It was headed in a straight line over the house. I thought my heart stopped. I couldn't move, I was in awe. I lost sight of the object after it passed over my home.
Summary: Disc like object with boomerang shaped light on front. Rest of the object was grey and dull.
